@InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5283

### Register User
POST {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login User
POST {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Analyze Repository (replace 1 with actual userId)
POST {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://github.com/microsoft/vscode",
  "id": 1
}

###

### Get User History (replace 1 with actual userId)
GET {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/api/analyze/history/me?userId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Forgot Password
POST {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "oldPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword456",
  "newPasswordConfirmation": "newpassword456"
}

###

GET {{InclusiveCode.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###
